POD1000000004_S0000067	That right there is the spirit of entrepreneurship.
POD1000000004_S0000068	I think the question is then, is this a legitimately huge problem? And is this a problem that a lot of people have as well?
POD1000000004_S0000069	For Salzburg and Pappas, the answer to both of those questions was an enthusiastic yes. Now, at this point, it was 2012, and T. Anders Company had been around for five years and was growing steadily.
