POD1000000010_S0000219	and they improve with practice.
POD1000000010_S0000220	Yeah, and starting these kinds of conversations early is crucial to raising a child who runs to help when somebody's hurt.
POD1000000010_S0000221	So, remember that small study we mentioned of kids on the playground?
