POD1000000010_S0000223	When one child heard another, many of the mothers responded with something casual and bland.
POD1000000010_S0000224	Yeah, like, oh, don't do that.
POD1000000010_S0000225	But the researchers found that the moms of the helper kids, those one in three who ran to help, they were different.
POD1000000010_S0000226	Yeah, they were warm and nurturing, but they also took it really seriously when their child hurt another child.
